{"tid":1330604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民政局周五與中學生聚會取消","createTime":"2019-07-18T15:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T15:36:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f878f53c206f03346293d671191693d6af23be","tid":1330604,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"民政事務局今晚（18日）回覆查詢表示，政府將不會在明天（19日，周五）舉辦青年人與官員的聚會。發言人表示，政府會透過不同途徑接觸不同背景人士，包括年輕人，以廣泛聆聽不同意見。 <br />\n<br />\n連登討論區早前有網民表示，有民政事務局人員聯絡中學生，表示民政事務局周五有聚會，屆時有機會與政務司長張建宗和特首林鄭月娥見面，又表示該人員沒有交代目的，只稱希望學生「發表自己意見」，並強調不會有記者出席。消息人士曾指出，政府當日的確有此聚會安排。惟消息傳出後，學生動源即在facebook呼籲學生切勿參與政府的閉門會面，不排除當日號召市民到場抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190718/s00001/1563459128525/%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E5%B1%80%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%81%9A%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190718%2Fs00001%2F1563459128525%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2581%259A%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=1bab8c72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190718%2Fs00001%2F1563459128525%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2581%259A%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588&h=7b7288a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190718/s00001/1563459128525/%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E5%B1%80%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%81%9A%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88</a>"}]}